<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Placement Portal</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #0f172a;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
    }

    nav {
      background-color: #1e293b;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
    }

    nav h2 {
      color: #38bdf8;
      margin: 0;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #94a3b8;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #38bdf8;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 50px 20px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #38bdf8;
    }

    .section p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .features {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .feature-box {
      background-color: #1e293b;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
      width: 280px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .feature-box:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.25);
    }

    .feature-box h3 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #7dd3fc;
    }

    .feature-box p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #cbd5e1;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <h2>Placement Portal</h2>
    <a href="/home">Login</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>About the Portal</h2>
    <p>
      The Placement Portal is a centralized platform where students can explore placement statistics 
      and company representatives can manage recruitment data efficiently.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Key Featuress</h2>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature-box">
        <h3>View Placement Recordss</h3>
        <p>Students can check placement stats and filter data year-wise or branch-wise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-box">
        <h3>Upload Company Data</h3>
        <p>Company users can post job roles, eligibility, and placement stats.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-box">
        <h3>Search & Filter</h3>
        <p>Smart filtering based on packages, companies, and roles.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-box">
        <h3>Secure Access</h3>
        <p>Separate login flows for students and companies for protected data access.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
